OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatches of low cloud will
OL,6,Flinger this morning, but this will
OL,7,Fgradually break up through the
OL,8,Fmorning. Hot, dry and sunny in the
OL,9,Fafternoon with light winds across the
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry, bright and warm
OL,13,Fevening. Patchy low cloud may spread
OL,14,Fback in overnight giving some areas of
OL,15,Fmist. Dry and warm overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FAny low cloud will quickly
OL,18,Flift and break to bring another hot
OL,19,Fand sunny day with light winds.
OL,20,FFeeling hot in the strong sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
